text: Functional: named constants [EENELC) su(eggs, sugari, wine, cheese, cream, fingers, espresso, sugar2, cocoa) beaten_eggs - beat(eggs) [P TTERRGEE(ToET CT o RTT E Lg I T) whisked - whisk(mixture) beaten_cheese - beat(cheese) cheese_mixture - beat(whisked, beaten_cheese) whipped_cream - whip(cream) folded_mixture - fold(cheese_mixture, whipped_cream) sweet_espresso - dissolve(sugar2, espresso) wet_fingers - soak(fingers, sweet_espresso, seconds: 2) assembled - assemble(folded_mixture, wet_fingers) complete - sift(assembled, cocoa) ready._tiramisu - refrigerate(complete) ready._tiramisu end
